{"abstract": "Businesses are planning to use a new tax arrangement to provide financing for energy efficiency upgrades with no upfront cost.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/20/business/energy-environment/tax-plan-to-turn-old-buildings-green-finds-favor.html", "snippet": "Businesses are planning to use a new tax arrangement to provide financing for energy efficiency upgrades with no upfront cost.", "lead_paragraph": "A business consortium that includes Lockheed Martin and Barclays bank plans to invest as much as $650 million over the next few years to slash the energy consumption of buildings in the Miami and Sacramento areas. It is the most ambitious effort yet to jump-start a national market for energy upgrades that many people believe could eventually be worth billions.", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "1", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2011/09/20/business/CARBON1_span/CARBON-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 350, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2011/09/20/business/CARBON1_span/CARBON-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 350}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2011/09/20/business/CARBON1_span/CARBON-jumbo.jpg", "height": 660, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2011/09/20/business/CARBON1_span/CARBON-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbStandard", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2011/09/20/business/CARBON1_span/CARBON-thumbStandard.jpg", "thumbnailwidth": 75, "thumbnailheight": 75}}], "headline": {"main": "Tax Plan to Turn Old Buildings \u2018Green\u2019 Finds Favor", "kicker": null, "content_kicker": null, "pr